---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero — all mono, terminal/docs aesthetic -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-20 pb-12 sm:pt-24 sm:pb-16 text-center font-mono">
    <p class="animate-hero text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gh-blue" style="animation-delay: 0ms;">
      // ai automation engineer
    </p>

    <h1 class="animate-hero mt-6 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gh-fg sm:text-4xl" style="animation-delay: 80ms;">
      AI automation for<br class="hidden sm:inline" /> business operations
    </h1>

    <p class="animate-hero mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted sm:text-base" style="animation-delay: 160ms;">
      Twenty years of hands-on engineering, applied to email, documents, and workflow integration.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- What I build — three numbered columns, mono everywhere -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-16 sm:pb-20 font-mono">
    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-8">

      <a href="/expertise#email" class="animate-on-scroll group block" style="transition-delay: 0ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>01</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg group-hover:text-gh-green transition-colors">
          email &amp; communication
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          Triage, classification, and automated replies for inbound business email. LLM with retrieval over an internal knowledge base.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/expertise#documents" class="animate-on-scroll group block" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>02</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg group-hover:text-gh-green transition-colors">
          document processing
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          Structured extraction from invoices, contracts, and forms. Auto-routing to the system of record, with confidence scoring.
        </p>
      </a>

      <a href="/expertise#workflows" class="animate-on-scroll group block" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>03</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg group-hover:text-gh-green transition-colors">
          workflow integration
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          ERP, email, and document stores connected so approvals, orders, and reports run end-to-end without a person in the middle.
        </p>
      </a>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why hire me — grid of credibility points -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-24 sm:pb-32">
    <p class="animate-on-scroll text-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gh-blue" style="transition-delay: 0ms;">
      // why hire me
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-x-12 sm:gap-y-14">

      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>04</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg">
          twenty years of production engineering
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          From data-center infrastructure to global payment systems to production AI agents. Built and shipped at every scale.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>05</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg">
          full-stack AI, end-to-end
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          Architecture, backend, LLM layer, IaC, deployment. One engineer, the whole pipeline &mdash; no handoffs, no missing pieces.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 240ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>06</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg">
          production over prototypes
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          Live agents handling real business email &mdash; not slide decks, not sandbox demos. The site you&rsquo;re reading is part of the proof.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 320ms;">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 text-xs text-gh-fg-subtle">
          <span>07</span>
          <span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gh-border"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gh-fg">
          pattern-matching across domains
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-relaxed text-gh-fg-muted">
          Payments, real estate, logistics, manufacturing. The bottlenecks repeat across industries; the fixes generalize.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
